title: Fresh INN
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual deli/cafe within the Holmpassage mall. Has fresh juice, smoothies, soy milk for coffee, and prepared foods in a glass case with sandwiches, a grilled veggie salad, sandwich with avocado, veggie-wrap. All the baked goods are vegan (cakes and muffins).
